Package: bibledit
Architecture: any
Depends: bibledit-data, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Bible editor
 A tool for the Bible translator.
 Translate Bibles.
 Edit Bibles.
 Proofread Bibles.
 Publish Bibles.
 Synchronize your data through Bibledit Cloud.

Package: bibledit-data
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: fonts-sil-ezra
Description: Data for bibledit
 Contains pictures, icons, lexicons, scripts.
 This is normally not installed manually.
 The bibledit package will install it automatically.
